articles.headline: AC Milan stunned by Sassuolo to slip to second successive league loss
articles.description: AC Milan slipped to their second successive Serie A defeat when Sassuolo stunned their opponents in the San Siro with a 3-1 comeback win.

articles.headline: AC Milan's Junior Messias' improbable rise to Champions League reminds us why we love sports
articles.description: Junior Messias appearing from obscurity to keep AC Milan's Champions League hopes alive is the culmination of his incredible journey.

articles.headline: The incredible story of AC Milan goalscorer Junior Messias
articles.description: Gab Marcotti reacts to the improbable story of ex-delivery man Junior Messias scoring the game-winning goal for AC Milan vs. Atletico.
